<L>__{interior interview room day}
<A>__{gerald carver, 36, an ambitious government lawyer with a relaxed, vaguely hip manner, looks over the file of the ingratiating black officer sitting across the desk from him.}
<C>__{carver}
<D>__{officer leland? you know the difference between a black man and nigger?}
<A>__{leland is startled, insulted, but doesn't want to blow the interview. he smiles weakly, shakes his head no.}
<C>__{carver}
<P>__{(continuing; pleasant smile)}
<D>__{yeah, most niggers don't.}
<A>__{stung, leland tries to laugh. carver puts his file aside, picks up another.}
<C>__{carver}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{nice to meet you.}
